# Reusable UI Primitives

Always check these existing components before building new UI. Import from `@/components/ui/`.

## Modal
`Modal` — base portal modal with overlay, escape/click-outside closing, optional title bar.
```tsx
import { Modal } from "@/components/ui/Modal";
<Modal isOpen={open} onClose={close} title="Edit Entry"
  panelClassName="w-full max-w-md rounded-xl border bg-background p-4 shadow-xl md:p-6">
  {children}
</Modal>
```
Props: `isOpen`, `onClose`, `title?`, `closeOnOverlayClick?`, `closeOnEscape?`, `showCloseButton?`, `overlayClassName?`, `panelClassName?`

## ConfirmModal
`ConfirmModal` — confirmation dialog (wraps Modal). Variants: `"danger"` | `"default"`.
```tsx
import { ConfirmModal } from "@/components/ui/ConfirmModal";
<ConfirmModal isOpen={show} onClose={cancel} onConfirm={handleDelete}
  message="This cannot be undone." variant="danger" isLoading={deleting} />
```

## PhotoLightbox
`PhotoLightbox` — full-screen image viewer with zoom, pan, pinch, keyboard nav.
```tsx
import { PhotoLightbox } from "@/components/ui/PhotoLightbox";
<PhotoLightbox images={urls} initialIndex={0} onClose={close} />
```

## ToggleGroup
`ToggleGroup` — segmented toggle buttons (e.g., Cards/Details/Map views).
```tsx
import { ToggleGroup } from "@/components/ui/ToggleGroup";
<ToggleGroup options={[{ value: "cards", label: "Cards", icon: <Grid /> }]} value={view} onChange={setView} />
```

## InfoCard
`InfoCard` — section card with title, icon, and content.
```tsx
import { InfoCard } from "@/components/ui/InfoCard";
<InfoCard title="Details" icon={<Info />}>{content}</InfoCard>
```

## SuggestionPicker
`SuggestionPicker` — searchable dropdown for string suggestions with clear button.
```tsx
import { SuggestionPicker } from "@/components/ui/SuggestionPicker";
<SuggestionPicker value={selected} onChange={setSelected} suggestions={items} placeholder="Filter..." />
```

## PageHeader (shared component)
`PageHeader` — consistent page header with icon, title, subtitle, desktop/mobile actions.
```tsx
import { PageHeader } from "@/components/PageHeader";
<PageHeader title="Feature" subtitle="Description" icon={<Icon className="h-5 w-5 md:h-6 md:w-6" />}
  iconWrapperClassName="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br from-emerald-500 to-emerald-600 text-white shadow-lg md:h-12 md:w-12"
  desktopAction={<button>Add</button>} />
```
